---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy">
    <div class="py-24 bg-white">
        <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
            <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-slate-900 font-serif mb-8">
                Privacy Policy
            </h1>
            <div class="prose prose-slate max-w-none">
                <p class="text-slate-600 mb-6">
                    Last updated: February 16, 2026
                </p>

                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-8 mb-4">
                    1. Introduction
                </h2>
                <p class="text-slate-600 mb-4">
                    LienSign ("we", "our", or "us") is committed to protecting
                    your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect,
                    use, and safeguard your information when you use our
                    service.
                </p>

                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-8 mb-4">
                    2. Information Handling
                </h2>
                <p class="text-slate-600 mb-4">
                    LienSign is a local-first application. The information you
                    provide (such as taxpayer ID, project details, and
                    signatures) is stored locally in your browser's persistent
                    storage. We do not transmit this data to any servers.
                </p>

                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-8 mb-4">
                    3. No Data Collection
                </h2>
                <p class="text-slate-600 mb-4">
                    We do not collect personal information on our servers. Since
                    there are no accounts or cloud-based processing, we do not
                    have access to the documents you generate.
                </p>

                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-8 mb-4">
                    4. Data Security
                </h2>
                <p class="text-slate-600 mb-4">
                    We implement industry-standard security measures to protect
                    your data. However, no method of transmission over the
                    internet is 100% secure.
                </p>

                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-8 mb-4">
                    5. Contact Us
                </h2>
                <p class="text-slate-600 mb-4">
                    If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please
                    contact us at support@liensign.com.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</Layout>
